<section class="content">
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Find your UDID</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Connect your iOS device to your Mac or PC.</li>
      <li>Open Finder (macOS Catalina+) or iTunes.</li>
      <li>Click your device, then click on the serial number to reveal the UDID.</li>
      <li>Copy the UDID and paste it back on the signing form.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>You can also use trusted third-party websites to fetch UDID via mobileconfig profiles.</p>
  </div>
</section>
